{"title":"统一身份认证","shareable":true,"id":"guide/account/authorize/index","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"info","text":["2023 级起，新生需要自己完成账号激活。"]},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"账号激活","icon":"account","url":"activate"}]},{"tag":"text","type":"tip","text":["2023 级研究生新生可立即激活。","2023 级本科新生需等到 8 月 15 日以后。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"获得学号"},{"tag":"text","text":["账号激活中需用到学号，学号是 10 位数字，您收到的录取通知书证书编号和日后发放的校园卡💳卡号即是学号。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"统一身份认证管理"},{"tag":"text","text":["如需管理自己的统一身份认证账号，请访问 https://authserver.nenu.edu.cn/authserver/login 并使用学号与设置的密码进行登录。"]},{"tag":"action","header":"校内地址","content":"https://authserver.nenu.edu.cn/authserver/login"},{"tag":"action","header":"校外地址","content":"https://authserver-443.webvpn.nenu.edu.cn/authserver/login"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/account/authserver.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["登录后，您可以在“个人资料中”额外绑定邮箱以供密码找回 (邮箱请绑定第三方邮箱)，并且可以修改密码。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/account/reset-password.jpg","desc":"修改密码","watermark":true}],"time":"2023 年 7 月 31 日 16:50:05"}